## Important Notes About the File

### File Location
The `.env.local` file MUST be in the **root of your project**, at the same level as:
- `package.json`
- `next.config.js`
- `app/` folder

**❌ Wrong locations:**
- Inside `app/` folder
- Inside `lib/` folder
- Inside any subfolder

**✅ Correct location:**
```
clausify/
├── .env.local          ← HERE!
├── package.json
└── next.config.js